  "title": "Transport Operations Executive",
  "description": "<p>We are looking for a responsible and dedicated Operations Executive to manage our fleet of vehicles. Job scope as follows:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Compile all bookings and place on the booking system</li>\n  <li>Schedule assignements for driver</li>\n  <li>Follow up with drivers on all assignments and ensure all are punctual services are delivered</li>\n  <li>Plan and maintain all vehicle inspection, road tax/Insurance renewal</li>\n  <li>Conduct check on vehicles for safety and ensure vehicle are up to standards. Report to office on defects</li>\n  <li>Ensure daily movements are updated and send to accounts deparment</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Candidate must have decent knowledge of Windows and Excel. Good in English.</p>\n<p>Company will provide mobile and computer. Incentives,Medical,Bonuses and annual leave will be given.</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Intrested candidates, kindly Whatsapp: 90053861 or 94558268</li>\n</ul>",
